verbose_text: Cytokines are key mediators of septic and aseptic inflammation and, given its important role in coordinating CNS responses to systemic inflammation [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR], the pro inflammatory cytokine IL-1beta might be predicted equally to underlie infection- and sterile inflammation induced cognitive dysfunction.
